@startuml
actor User
participant Browser
participant API
database DB

User -> Browser: Ввод логина/пароля
Browser -> API: POST /api/login
API -> DB: SELECT user by username
DB --> API: user + password_hash
API -> API: VerifyPassword + BuildJWT
API --> Browser: 200 { token, user }

Browser -> API: GET /api/me (Bearer token)
API -> API: ParseJWT
API --> Browser: 200 user claims
@enduml

